headline: 3 Reasons KEYS is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Although the S&P 500 is down 9.9% over the past six months, Keysight’s stock price has fallen further to $131.95, losing shareholders 17% of their capital. This might have investors contemplating their next move.
